name: How Humans Expect Sincerity
description:
The pure white light of the infinite and inexhaustible God Almighty, can be reached and requested by mankind, and is expected by action and prayer with time.

But alas.. the shadows of their mind and lust make the light is biased in infinity. The colors are the result of human conscience itself which confines the white and repeats itself endlessly. And Finally, the eternal question arises, can the full white ball be achieved?

3500x4870px
